"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750934","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-07-18","<p>It is planned that the Defence Fulfilment Centre will become fully operational in March 2019.</p>","West Worcestershire","Harriett Baldwin",,"2017-07-18T14:37:01.893Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750934/answer","Biography information for Harriett Baldwin","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750934/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/750934/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-07-11","Defence Fulfilment Centre: Donnington","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, when he expects the Defence Fulfilment Centre in Donnington to be fully operational.","false","Biography information for Deidre Brock","Edinburgh North and Leith","Deidre  Brock","4291"
